channel.name: Decentralized Drug Listings
channel.description:
A ZeroVoat channel for decentralized drug trading.

Post your items for sell or browse for items to buy.

Vendors who list items please include your PGP Address on your listings so that buyers can verify you from other fallen markets.

ALWAYS PGP ENCRYPT YOUR ADDRESSES!
